text: Khristo Traykov (born 24 September 1947) is a Bulgarian wrestler. He competed at the 1968 Summer Olympics and the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Bulgaria Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:People from Sofia Province
